      "description": "Looking for your next great project? This vehicle is the perfect canvas for a mechanic or a DIY enthusiast ready to bring a car back to life! While it definitely needs some significant TLC and mechanical attention, it offers a fantastic, budget-friendly entry point for someone looking to roll up their sleeves and get to work. Grab this opportunity to own a vehicle with potential at a fraction of the cost!",
